ðŸš€ Getting Started
-----------------

1) Clone the repo
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/safeway.git

2) Frontend
cd client  
npm install  
npm run dev  

3) Backend
cd server  
npm install  

Create .env

DATABASE_URL=  
JWT_SECRET=  
OPENROUTE_API_KEY=  
TWILIO_SID=  
TWILIO_AUTH_TOKEN=  
TWILIO_FROM=  
REDIS_URL=  

Run:

npx prisma migrate dev  
npm run dev  

